ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Highly recommend this course if you are into systems and network programming at all. Its just great although make sure you have free time as its a decent amount of work.
I recommend it considering it provides programming practice and it is not that hard to follow.
Yes, I would recommend to another student.
